msgctxt "21337012-0-2394"
msgid "(Battle Chant of the Intrepid Two Hundred)"
"\n"
"\nWe are dragon knights. We are dragons. "
"\n"
"\nIf you attack us, you will meet talons."
"\n"
"\nIf you strike us, you will eat spikes."
"\n"
"\nIf you injure us, our wounds will close."
"\n"
"\nIf you anger us, you will burn. "
"\n"
"\nIf you run from us, we will pounce upon you."
"\n"
"\nYou cannot win. We cannot lose."
"\n"
"\nWe are dragon knights. We are dragons."
msgstr "(不敵なる200人の戦歌)\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らはドラゴンナイト。我らはドラゴン。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らを攻撃するなら、鉤爪が迎え撃つ。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らを殴るなら、鋭いトゲを食らう。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らを傷付けても、傷口はふさがる。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らの怒りを買うなら、炎に包まれる。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らから逃げ出しても、後を追って捕まえる。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\nお前は勝てない。我らは負けない。\\r"
"\n\\r"
"\n我らはドラゴンナイト。我らはドラゴン。"

